      <title>非洲疾病预防控制中心预计 Mpox 疫苗将于下周结束前抵达</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/africa-cdc-sees-mpox-vaccines-arriving-before-end-of-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲主要卫生咨询机构上周宣布，非洲痘疫情为非洲大陆公共卫生紧急事件。预计痘苗将在未来几天抵达非洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/africa-cdc-sees-mpox-vaccines-arriving-before-end-of-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:28:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外交部称阿塞拜疆正式申请加入金砖国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/azerbaijan-formally-applies-to-join-brics-foreign-ministry-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴库外交部发言人艾克桑·哈西扎达周二在电话中表示，阿塞拜疆已正式申请成为金砖国家（由中国和俄罗斯领导的新兴市场国家集团）成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/azerbaijan-formally-applies-to-join-brics-foreign-ministry-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:17:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
